Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要下船 让我下船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了 就要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我振作些 浓眉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯晕船了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的大浪确实扛不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…让船不要摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晕船而已嘛 真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 但这样晃真扛不住啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先找个地方休息 等天气好转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然和预定的航线有些偏离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但东边应该有座小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说我倒想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中立海域的无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…对 是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去这儿吧 去避避…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及了 赶紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转舵 向东北方航向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪确实很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当厉害啊 大家都要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让凯老师稍事休息 所以才来这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们又执行什么任务呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是根据纲手大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去东海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四次忍界大战很快就要开战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要准备充足的秘药以及兵粮丸的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七草岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是药草的宝库
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地图上标有药草所在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曼陀罗草 活力人参 红蝾螈 大蔓藤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是什么都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如有余力去看看也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切不可勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小樱就成了队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯老师睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万事准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时随地可以出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少了鹿丸的十班残余啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是残余呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是多余的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们七班不也是少了鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是各做各的去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐井应该也去执行其他任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都有自己的任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都不用做没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来有很重大的任务等着鸣人去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次出航也是为了这个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也要等凯老师恢复后才能出航
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如帮帮我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采药草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是 采草而已 游刃有余吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 都多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在看什么呢 完全不对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完全摸不清头脑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如和他们两人一起照看凯老师的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想等凯先生恢复后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商讨一下航海日程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 留下也没啥事做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 以这个作参考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦战争开始的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定会有伤者出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数百人…数千人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了治疗那些伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是绝对要完成的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人明明说这里是药草的宝库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象中的难找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要换个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往更高处走走看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得找兵粮丸的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 记住味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 干活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吧…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗…不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该是这个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这味道好像不太一样 又好像有点相似
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪 这种地方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会生长着曼陀罗草的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是气候起变化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是活力人参
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 还是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长了一堆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做出很不错的兵粮丸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敬了 那边的活力人参是我们先发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个护额 看来是木叶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大国之人是不会在意我们这些小国的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们乃南边红州岛的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是上忍 坂东
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下忍 佐田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是木地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传言战争临近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便前来这座小岛收集药草
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 难怪怎么找都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为你们捷足先登了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 已经收集一大部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样一来你们就该苦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是帮了忍者联军的大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我算 我算 我算算算…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一束这个价位如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的人真不好商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我好好学习学习…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要收钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是送给我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了小的们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这样的小国是生存不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 木叶若不愿意购买的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就指望其他村里的大名殿下们出资了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争中会受伤的不只是忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…明知道如此还做买卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不也是靠任务赚钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分出级别 标上价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了…无论如何敬请谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也需要挣回自我防御的资金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔一株为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔两株为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔三株为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔四株为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就无法完成任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这样说 又不能半路抢劫他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然 都组成忍者联军了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能和其他村子的忍者发生纠纷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 没啥好苦恼的 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座岛是药草的宝库对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说这附近被他们抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没啥了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您所说极是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来才是珍稀物品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过不是那么容易采集到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有个棘手的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么暂且告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了药草为何肚子会疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药草
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会是误吃了毒草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近应该长着大蔓藤才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经被采掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快 再慢点什么都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蔓藤的花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是还留着一些嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 那些家伙不是给我们留了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下的是为了播种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采草不除根是采药草的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 不是为了我们留的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去下一个吧 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去河流上游找红蝾螈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 写着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勿过此桥 红州专用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么不要过桥 我就过给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 肚子也好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体麻痹得动弹不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这卷起的不是麻痹草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是个圈套 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管那个了…救…救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到红蝾螈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 红蝾螈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来就这么一只
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这尺寸不过是个娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能放生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪时间被平白无故地浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 怎能这么悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧去下一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得是谁让我们这么悠闲的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已经没戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 只能去这里了 地狱谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从地底涌出的泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是能治疗撞伤 刀伤 扭伤等等的万能泥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是纲手大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里若有余力去看看也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切不可勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是相当危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去地狱谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别老是做偷鸡摸狗的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能对木叶的各位做那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是做采集药草的准备罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不跟你们一般见识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到万能泥浆就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 又想拖住我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是无偿服务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦斯会时不时地喷出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是毒气 长时间接触的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是无规则的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样才能得到深处的万能泥浆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多重影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 万能泥浆 我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫  没工具拿不走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:16:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是个大赌博啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能碰运气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本就行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏您 总算确认好路线了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做生意可不是抱着玩玩的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了小国的生存 我们也得拼死努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等瓦斯消失后就上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁.大突破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁之术 挺能干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁.大突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光跑来不及的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁.大…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欠下大国的情 之后不知道要赔多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会要钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一直对我们小国…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说这是无偿服务了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大玉螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 该怎么说呢 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 真的不收钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早说是免费的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是他国的忍者 也不全是敌对的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候也突破利益关系携手合作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的忍者联军就是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐田 木地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像真是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀着感恩的心来接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是来自我们的免费服务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收下这万能泥浆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边所有已经采集好的药草也请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就算我们送给忍者联军的礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 任务完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 你才是 今天深受启发了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 你们也加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样合适吗 坂东大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在给联军一个恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃点小亏就能得到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会了 大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时的离别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你 我的身体已经能适应船了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 加油啊 特别任务加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,听说每到浓雾天气时就会出现那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为了引导死者的灵魂 乌鸦作为先导出现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,帆柱上点亮的巨大鬼火就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,便会踏上前往死者国度的航程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传 被诅咒的幽灵船
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 出现了
